Insider Activity


Individual




Mary Ann Tocio



Ms. Mary A. Tocio is Independent Director at Civitas Solutions, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Burlington Stores, Inc., Civitas Solutions, Inc., Bright Horizons Family Solutions, Inc., Harvard Pilgrim Health Care, Inc., Horizons for Homeless Children, Inc., Ella Health, Inc., Carewell Industries, Inc., and Dana-Farber Cancer Institute, Inc.
Ms. Tocio was previously employed as Independent Director by Mac-Gray Corp., President, Chief Operating Officer & Director by Bright Horizons Family Solutions LLC, and Senior Vice President-Operations by Health Stop Medical Management, Inc. She also served on the board at Zany Brainy, Inc.
She received her MBA from Simmons College (Massachusetts).



